<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='682000' id='t-682000'>This is Dr. Fan Jianchuan.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='685000' id='t-685000'>Jianchuan comes from Sichuan Province</span>
