<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>and what his life has been like</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697000' id='t-697000'>over the last 50 tumultuous years.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700000' id='t-700000'>He's been a soldier, a teacher,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>a politician, a vice-mayor</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704000' id='t-704000'>and a business man.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706000' id='t-706000'>But if you sat down and asked him, &quot;Who are you really,</span>
