<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711000' id='t-711000'>He would tell you, &quot;I'm a collector,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='714000' id='t-714000'>and I curate a museum.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='716000' id='t-716000'>I was lucky; I had heard about him for years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='718000' id='t-718000'>and I finally met him earlier this year</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720000' id='t-720000'>at his museum in Chengdu.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='723000' id='t-723000'>He's been a collector all of his life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726000' id='t-726000'>starting when he was four or five in the early 1960's.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729000' id='t-729000'>Now, just think of the early 1960's in China.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732000' id='t-732000'>Over a lifetime, through everything,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='735000' id='t-735000'>through the Cultural Revolution and everything afterward,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738000' id='t-738000'>he's kept collecting,</span>
